                "$$u_n = \\dfrac{n^2(3 + \\frac{5}{n} - \\frac{1}{n^2})}{n^2(2 - \\frac{1}{n} + \\frac{7}{n^2})} = \\dfrac{3 + \\frac{5}{n} - \\frac{1}{n^2}}{2 - \\frac{1}{n} + \\frac{7}{n^2}}$$",
