                "**Théorème 3 (Gendarmes) :** Si $\\displaystyle\\lim_{n \\to +\\infty} u_n = \\displaystyle\\lim_{n \\to +\\infty} w_n = \\ell$, alors $\\displaystyle\\lim_{n \\to +\\infty} v_n = \\ell$"
